name: MODERN FAMILY
description:
Mason Storm's take on the fabulous classic painting by Norman Rockwell.
This A2 print is a copy of Mason's original oil painting and is beautifully reproduced on high quality fine art paper with archival inks.

Signed and numbered by the artist

Limited to an edition of 100 worldwide with 2 Artists Proofs

Mason's pint runs sell out very quickly and this new series is bound to be snapped up fast!
